<h3 id="resources">Resources</h3>

<ul>
	<li>Something that may help is our free Extension for The Events Calendar, <a href="https://theeventscalendar.com/extensions/allow-only-location-time-zones-for-events/" rel="noopener" target="_blank"><em>Allow Only Location-Based Time Zones for Events</em></a>, to <strong>ensure</strong> that UTC offsets are never used in your events. This may help to reduce confusing time outputs.</li>
</ul></div>    			
